# Hospital Management System (C)

## Overview
This is a simple Hospital Management System implemented in C.
It allows users to manage patient records through a menu-driven interface.

The system stores patient data in a file for permanent storage.

## Features
- Add new patient
- Display all patients
- Search patient by ID
- Store records using file handling

## Technologies Used
- C Programming Language
- File Handling
- Structures
- Functions
- Menu Driven Interface

## Data Stored
Each patient record contains:
- Patient ID
- Name
- Age
- Disease

